Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去了 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回来的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那云彩是什么啊
