Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我头直疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俱胝102 位置不变
